snippet.textDisplay: I would like to dedicate this song to our brave men and youth fighting in Kashmir for their sovereignty, fearlessly. I would also dedicate this beautiful anthem to our brave soldiers fighting all the forces of the world who're trying to destroy our country. fighting our external and internal enemies so that you and I can enjoy freedom and live as a sovereign nation in this world. Nara-e-Taqbeer, Allahoakbar. Nara-e-haidery, Ya Ali. Pakistan zindabad!

snippet.textDisplay: As an Indian let me just add my voice in support of Sundar Disilva. To carry hate is a choice that I refuse to make.
